ygData.messageBody:
Salutations!

I know this is way late in a reply but I have not been
up on checking e-mail in a while.
I found that fishing and cooking worked well for my
cleric . . . and by the way, she dinged 65 last night
. . .
:o)
I could fish, then I bought the bat wings and made
fish rolls. After that I went to PoS and fished for
storm trout and those make food also to get your
baking over 200 and get your fishing up at the same
time. It takes a bit of patience, but even with buying
bat wings it took very little plat. It helped a lot
though to have a high wis character. My cleric
definately skills up faster then my poor Ranger.
:o)
Bran (Buttercup)
